data.description:
The newly renovated Seagate is the only resort in Delray offering guests exclusive access to a private beach with new beachfront dining, Atlantic Avenue's most spacious guestrooms, a championship golf course, full-service spa, two swimming pools, and the all-new Bourbon Steak by Michelin starred chef Michel Mina, now open.

We are home to Atlantic Avenue’s most spacious all-new guestrooms. Thoughtfully reimagined with a fresh, coastal elegance, each of our 157 rooms and suites features designer furnishings, original artwork, and spa-inspired bathrooms with walk-in showers. Whether you’re here to unwind or explore, every detail is crafted with your ideal getaway in mind.

You may view all of our current openings and apply online here: https://workforcenow.adp.com/mascsr/default/mdf/recruitment/recruitment.html?cid=a94fcd62-86d1-4b42-a51b-dc9182f61fbe
